 r‚ÜêTest_05_BadTransaction base_url;after;before;h;payload;res
‚çù Send a POST where second row violates a NOT NULL constraint (empty `type` ‚Üí NULL bind ‚Üí server-side rejection).
‚çù Transact error-guard: the first row's insert must be rolled back, and the HTTP response shows the SQAPL/server error message.

 before‚Üê#.DCMS.SQL.Do'SELECT COUNT(*) FROM event_type'

